Title: Integration Testing ASP.NET Core 6 Minimal APIs
Description: This post is about implementing integration testing in ASP.NET Core Minimal APIs. Usually when I talk about Minimal APIs, one of the question I used to get is how to implement integration testing and I saw some questions related to this in Stack Overflow as well. In this blog post I am trying to cover implementing ASP.NET Core integration testing with NUnit Framework. This code is can be used in XUnit as well.
